        "title": "Add COE root-cause skill",
        "body": "## Summary\n\nAdds a bundled `coe-root-cause` skill for Correction of Error root-cause analysis.\n\nThe skill gives agents a concrete workflow for recurring failures, false success, missed work, data loss, and brittle automation: classify the failure, preserve evidence safely, build a timeline, run 5+ Whys, define corrective actions, and verify before claiming closure.\n\n## Notes\n\n- Adds `skills/coe-root-cause/SKILL.md`.\n- Extends the bundled skill frontmatter smoke test to cover the new skill.\n- Keeps the workflow public-safe and asks agents to redact secrets, tokens, PII, customer data, and private workspace details.\n- Clarifies that report-only requests should propose corrective actions unless the user asks to apply them.\n\n## Verification\n\n- `env CI=1 OPENCLAW_TEST_PROJECTS_SERIAL=1 OPENCLAW_VITEST_NO_OUTPUT_TIMEOUT_MS=15000 node scripts/run-vitest.mjs run --config test/vitest/vitest.agents-core.config.ts src/agents/skills.bundled-frontmatter.test.ts`\n- Local AI review: no blockers.\n\n## Follow-up\n\nOne reviewer suggested a future stronger bundled-skill contract that enumerates all `skills/*/SKILL.md` files and checks directory/name consistency. I kept this PR minimal and limited the test change to frontmatter smoke coverage for the new bundled skill.\n",
